<div class="post-entry">
<h4 id="pc19708" class="entry-title hn">Re: Wii/Wii U homebrew viral code?</h4>
<div class="entry-content">
<p>We can target .DOLs and .WADs as they&#039;re the most common. Themes tend to be embedded into System Menu sidegrades before application (because why the fuck not), so we could probably include .MYM and .CSM formats in there too.</p>
<div class="sig-content"><span class="sig-line"> </span>I like to examine and theorize about everything, from Amazon&#039;s &lt;quote&gt; impenetrable &lt;/quote&gt; ultravisor to autorun viruses (virii?) being technology&#039;s version of an STD (Slot Transmitted Disease). <br/>I dabble in Python 2.x and non-stereotypical BATCH (x&gt;50 lines). I also fuck up VMs from time to time.<br/><br/>┬──┬ ︵ /(.□. \）</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
